CallFire,is,an,online,text,and,voice,messaging,platform,designed,to,meet,the,needs,of,a,variety,of,users,and,organizations,The,platform,comes,with,APIs,for,integrating,its,functions,into,third,party,applications,and,services,The,CallFire,Postbacks,API,allows,developers,to,get,information,about,their,sent,messages,and,phone,calls,via,postbacks,Developers,will,need,a,website,capable,of,hosting,PHP,files,in,order,to,accept,the,postbacks